@startuml state-user-session

skinparam defaultFontName Liberation Sans
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

skinparam state {
  BorderColor #003087
  BackgroundColor #EEF3FA
  FontColor #003087
  ArrowColor #333333
  ArrowFontColor #555555
  ArrowFontSize 10
}

left to right direction

[*] --> Unauthenticated

Unauthenticated : entry / show login and register forms

Unauthenticated --> Authenticated : login [credentials valid] / issue JWT token (7-day TTL)

Authenticated : entry / store JWT in session state\ndo / unlock protected features (Simulate, My Matrices)

Authenticated --> Unauthenticated : logout / discard token from session
Authenticated --> Unauthenticated : token expires [TTL elapsed] / redirect to login

@enduml
